00:29:18.260 --> 00:29:18.760 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:29:18.760 --> 00:29:19.301 align:middle line:90%
>>OTHMER: OK.

00:29:19.301 --> 00:29:22.860 align:middle line:84%
