00:31:19.710 --> 00:31:22.465 align:middle line:84%
you like a dark cloud just
smashed you in the face.

00:31:22.465 --> 00:31:24.080 align:middle line:90%
It was just horrible.

00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:26.070 align:middle line:84%
