screwed up I was getting.

00:32:06.290 --> 00:32:08.090 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't say I
was reckless, but I

00:32:08.090 --> 00:32:14.760 align:middle line:84%
was some-- it just seemed
like I didn't care anymore.

00:32:14.760 --> 00:32:17.130 align:middle line:84%
