00:32:19.310 --> 00:32:20.550 align:middle line:90%
and they say, oh, yeah.

00:32:20.550 --> 00:32:21.050 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:32:21.050 --> 00:32:23.212 align:middle line:90%
Well, you might have PTSD.

00:32:23.212 --> 00:32:24.670 align:middle line:84%
Then I realized
there was something

00:32:24.670 --> 00:32:29.136 align:middle line:84%
