able to correct the situation.

00:32:29.136 --> 00:32:33.090 align:middle line:90%


00:32:33.090 --> 00:32:35.370 align:middle line:84%
I was really excited when I
heard about neurofeedback.

00:32:35.370 --> 00:32:37.750 align:middle line:84%
It was something new that
I'd never tried before.

00:32:37.750 --> 00:32:40.590 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to check it out--
see if that would work.

00:32:40.590 --> 00:32:43.520 align:middle line:84%
I mean, for me, it was more
like, what more could I lose?

00:32:43.520 --> 00:32:46.660 align:middle line:84%
At Camp Pendelton over
at the Navy hospital,

00:32:46.660 --> 00:32:49.000 align:middle line:90%
