00:33:54.266 --> 00:33:55.640 align:middle line:84%
Because beforehand,
I just seemed

00:33:55.640 --> 00:33:58.470 align:middle line:84%
like I was in a cocoon--
didn't want to break out,

00:33:58.470 --> 00:33:59.860 align:middle line:90%
didn't want to talk to anybody.

00:33:59.860 --> 00:34:01.720 align:middle line:84%
I noticed I was
able to focus more.

00:34:01.720 --> 00:34:03.830 align:middle line:84%
I was able to
concentrate, sleep better.

00:34:03.830 --> 00:34:07.770 align:middle line:84%
I was able to understand what I
needed to do and how to do it.

00:34:07.770 --> 00:34:10.510 align:middle line:84%
After neurofeedback,
