00:34:10.510 --> 00:34:12.830 align:middle line:84%
any medications or
herbal supplements.

00:34:12.830 --> 00:34:14.929 align:middle line:84%
>>And I've definitely
seen a difference, I mean,

00:34:14.929 --> 00:34:17.690 align:middle line:84%
compared to the herbal
medications and other things

00:34:17.690 --> 00:34:18.630 align:middle line:90%
