00:37:00.140 --> 00:37:03.030 align:middle line:84%
But if it's sending a
more coherent frequency,

00:37:03.030 --> 00:37:05.400 align:middle line:84%
then the picture
starts to widen.

00:37:05.400 --> 00:37:08.220 align:middle line:90%
Is that a good way of saying it?

00:37:08.220 --> 00:37:10.340 align:middle line:84%
>>OTHMER: At this
low frequency, yes,

00:37:10.340 --> 00:37:13.080 align:middle line:84%
