00:37:54.805 --> 00:37:57.520 align:middle line:90%


00:37:57.520 --> 00:37:58.260 align:middle line:90%
Or is it both?

00:37:58.260 --> 00:38:00.430 align:middle line:90%
>>OTHMER: It's both.

00:38:00.430 --> 00:38:06.690 align:middle line:84%
So the signal from the brain
is processed by the computer.

00:38:06.690 --> 00:38:10.180 align:middle line:84%
And then by virtue
of the imagery,

00:38:10.180 --> 00:38:12.860 align:middle line:84%
the information is also being
conveyed back to the brain.

00:38:12.860 --> 00:38:14.080 align:middle line:90%
So that's the feedback loop.

00:38:14.080 --> 00:38:14.860 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Feedback loop.

00:38:14.860 --> 00:38:15.020 align:middle line:90%
>>OTHMER: Right.

00:38:15.020 --> 00:38:15.620 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I understand.

00:38:15.620 --> 00:38:15.950 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:38:15.950 --> 00:38:16.616 align:middle line:90%
>>OTHMER: Right.

00:38:16.616 --> 00:38:18.570 align:middle line:84%
And now, the brain
operates that way

00:38:18.570 --> 00:38:21.430 align:middle line:84%
with lots of internal
feedback loops,

